rings the doorbell and runs away.]

2257
01:21:14,460 --> 01:21:14,670
[PM 2:32]

2258
01:21:14,670 --> 01:21:15,810
What is this?

2259
01:21:16,620 --> 01:21:16,730
[Bold Santa Sooji delivering the gift]

2260
01:21:16,730 --> 01:21:18,070
Who are you?

2261
01:21:18,200 --> 01:21:19,540
Who are you?

2262
01:21:19,750 --> 01:21:21,360
Who are you?

2263
01:21:21,610 --> 01:21:24,070
[2:34 PM]

2264
01:21:24,410 --> 01:21:24,860
[The first person
to deliver a gift — Dex!]

2265
01:21:24,860 --> 01:21:26,170
This is seriously…

2266
01:21:26,290 --> 01:21:27,450
Two minutes.

2267
01:21:27,630 --> 01:21:30,150
[If I'd gone to the right place,
I would've been first.]

2268
01:21:30,470 --> 01:21:31,810
[Oh?!]

2269
01:21:31,990 --> 01:21:34,200
[Dex, congratulations! A special video
will be revealed for Dex,]

2270
01:21:34,200 --> 01:21:36,420
[who delivered the first gift.]

2271
01:21:36,680 --> 01:21:38,050
[Amazing. Amazing!]

2272
01:21:38,330 --> 01:21:38,910
[Obtained the first-gift bonus]

2273
01:21:38,910 --> 01:21:39,770
Director.

2274
01:21:39,920 --> 01:21:41,230
Protein.

2275
01:21:42,470 --> 01:21:43,690
[Who is it?]

2276
01:21:44,600 --> 01:21:46,490
[Protein drink~?!]

2277
01:21:46,930 --> 01:21:50,360
[The only perk that lets you see
your Manito's reaction]

2278
01:21:50,670 --> 01:21:53,510
[Ahahaha, he got it~?]

2279
01:21:53,890 --> 01:21:55,030
[Hehe, I knew it.]

2280
01:21:55,030 --> 01:21:55,090
43 grams.

2281
01:21:55,090 --> 01:21:56,060
[Protein: 43 g]

2282
01:21:56,060 --> 01:21:56,240
I told you—he'd definitely pick
the one with the highest content.

2283
01:21:56,240 --> 01:21:58,530
[Exactly as expected.]

2284
01:21:58,960 --> 01:21:59,020
[Excited by the vivid reaction
to receiving the gift]

2285
01:21:59,020 --> 01:22:01,060
Why is he so relaxed?

2286
01:22:03,560 --> 01:22:03,680
Still, it's kind of reassuring.

2287
01:22:03,680 --> 01:22:05,290
[A gift delivery
filled with thrill and joy!]

2288
01:22:05,290 --> 01:22:07,350
Seeing how he reacted
when he got the gift…

2289
01:22:07,350 --> 01:22:09,270
[Short reply: Thanks
for the protein powder.]

2290
01:22:09,540 --> 01:22:11,030
[I just received it in my room.]

2291
01:22:11,340 --> 01:22:13,130
[Gift status]

2292
01:22:13,130 --> 01:22:16,060
[Gift status: Not received]

2293
01:22:17,010 --> 01:22:18,540
[Wait—hold on.]

2294
01:22:18,720 --> 01:22:21,800
[My Manito is totally silent~?]

2295
01:22:22,100 --> 01:22:24,640
[Suddenly remembers her own Manito]

2296
01:22:22,100 --> 01:22:22,100
Where is he?

2297
01:22:24,980 --> 01:22:26,830
[Is he…
off doing another schedule?]

2298
01:22:26,990 --> 01:22:28,800
[Doesn't know what's important anymore~]

2299
01:22:29,730 --> 01:22:32,010
[Ugh, the traffic is terrible…]

2300
01:22:32,310 --> 01:22:32,320
Decaf latte.

2301
01:22:32,320 --> 01:22:36,430
[Driving 40 minutes
to buy Sooji's favorite coffee]

2302
01:22:36,740 --> 01:22:38,710
You know that, right, hyung…?

2303
01:22:38,710 --> 01:22:40,750
[I don't drink coffee.]

2304
01:22:40,960 --> 01:22:41,050
Just to buy coffee.

2305
01:22:41,050 --> 01:22:43,510
[I've never been this desperate
just to buy coffee before…]

2306
01:22:43,510 --> 01:22:46,510
Coming out at this hour
this is my first time in my life.

2307
01:22:46,830 --> 01:22:48,320
[Rabbit~]

2308
01:22:48,860 --> 01:22:50,660
[I'm not that greedy.]

2309
01:22:50,840 --> 01:22:52,470
As long as it matches
her taste, that's enough.

2310
01:22:52,830 --> 01:22:54,500
[As for me…]

2311
01:22:54,710 --> 01:22:56,790
[What I'm thinking about now is—]

2312
01:22:56,950 --> 01:22:59,300
[An unexpected gift!]

2313
01:22:59,510 --> 01:22:59,550
[Plan 1: Rent a racetrack]

2314
01:22:59,550 --> 01:23:01,010
I want to rent a racetrack.

2315
01:23:01,110 --> 01:23:02,040
Then I can ride a motorcycle with him.

2316
01:23:02,040 --> 01:23:04,360
[Plan 2: Ride motorcycles together]

2317
01:23:04,570 --> 01:23:06,620
[Huh? The crew:
But gifts must be delivered]

2318
01:23:06,620 --> 01:23:08,680
[without revealing your identity…]

2319
01:23:09,080 --> 01:23:13,310
[Ah… we can't ride together?]

2320
01:23:13,790 --> 01:23:17,480
[Will Sunghoon be able
to deliver the gift safely…?]

2321
01:23:17,600 --> 01:23:17,710
Let's go.

2322
01:23:17,710 --> 01:23:18,720
[The uncle finally makes a move!]

2323
01:23:18,720 --> 01:23:18,840
[Choo pushes Plan 1: renting
a limited-edition motorcycle and track]

2324
01:23:18,840 --> 01:23:21,130
I want to book a racetrack
and ride motorcycles with him together.

2325
01:23:21,130 --> 01:23:21,460
[(Source: Dex socials)]

2326
01:23:21,460 --> 01:23:23,720
If we go racing together,
it'll be amazing.

2327
01:23:23,720 --> 01:23:24,960
[Hey, are you busy tomorrow?]

2328
01:23:24,960 --> 01:23:25,320
[Choo pushes Plan 2:
invite an international star]

2329
01:23:25,320 --> 01:23:26,210
I should be free.

2330
01:23:26,210 --> 01:23:26,340
[Choo pushes Plan 3: travel abroad too?]

2331
01:23:26,340 --> 01:23:27,880
Whether it's Japan or anywhere else,

2332
01:23:27,880 --> 01:23:29,340
we could do a two-day-one-night trip.

2333
01:23:29,340 --> 01:23:30,150
[Would that even work?]

2334
01:23:31,580 --> 01:23:31,680
[Hongchul has already
been driving for 8 hours]

2335
01:23:31,680 --> 01:23:33,950
[I don't even know if I'm a Manito
or just a chauffeur anymore.]

2336
01:23:33,950 --> 01:23:34,320
My Manito is completely silent.

2337
01:23:34,320 --> 01:23:35,220
[(Sooji)]

2338
01:23:35,220 --> 01:23:36,520
[Sooji, I'm here!!!]

2339
01:23:36,730 --> 01:23:38,150
I have to see
the reaction with my own eyes!

2340
01:23:38,210 --> 01:23:38,350
So nervous. So nervous.

2341
01:23:38,350 --> 01:23:40,270
[Trying to see the reaction —
but risking exposure?]

2342
01:23:40,460 --> 01:23:41,450
Can I lose control?

2343
01:23:41,450 --> 01:23:41,640
[Jennie's additional gift attack]

2344
01:23:41,640 --> 01:23:42,970
How should I ambush him?

2345
01:23:43,050 --> 01:23:43,190
I feel like I'm going to get caught.

2346
01:23:43,190 --> 01:23:44,630
[Boldly infiltrating Dex's base]

2347
01:23:44,890 --> 01:23:46,350
I think he's about to come out.

2348
01:23:46,350 --> 01:23:47,890
[Run! Run!]

2349
01:23:47,890 --> 01:23:48,620
What is this?

2350
01:23:48,940 --> 01:23:49,760
[Did they come here before?]

2351
01:23:49,760 --> 01:23:50,300
Did they?

2352
01:23:50,380 --> 01:23:51,950
[Stop right there!!!]

2353
01:23:51,950 --> 01:23:52,460
Whatever.

2354
01:23:52,460 --> 01:23:53,930
[The distance
between the two keeps closing]

2355
01:23:53,930 --> 01:23:55,630
He's really coming out—really.

2356
01:23:55,630 --> 01:23:57,060
[Can she avoid Dex's radar?]

2357
01:23:57,060 --> 01:23:58,790
[Emergency call
from Manito Club HQ]

2358
01:23:58,790 --> 01:23:59,910
We need to go to HQ.

2359
01:24:00,070 --> 01:24:02,110
Move, move.

2360
01:24:02,240 --> 01:24:03,100
Who's going to show up?

2361
01:24:03,100 --> 01:24:03,920
Oh wow.

2362
01:24:03,920 --> 01:24:04,220
[Manito Club members finally meet]

2363
01:24:04,220 --> 01:24:05,290
No. No.

2364
01:24:05,760 --> 01:24:07,110
Hello.

2365
01:24:07,200 --> 01:24:07,220
Everyone's here.

2366
01:24:07,220 --> 01:24:09,100
[A warm, cheerful atmosphere]

2367
01:24:10,010 --> 01:24:11,390
[That's what we thought… ]

2368
01:24:11,690 --> 01:24:13,170
[Say hello—this is Rabbit hyung.]

2369
01:24:13,400 --> 01:24:14,500
[No, no…]

2370
01:24:14,500 --> 01:24:15,160
Not Rabbit.

2371
01:24:15,180 --> 01:24:15,610
[Raccoon Dog!]

2372
01:24:16,450 --> 01:24:16,560
Jennie, why are you so shocked?

2373
01:24:16,560 --> 01:24:18,490
[Jennie, why are you reacting like that?]

2374
01:24:18,660 --> 01:24:20,420
[Please don't pay attention to me…]

2375
01:24:20,420 --> 01:24:20,510
What? I don't know.

2376
01:24:20,510 --> 01:24:21,820
[A duel to protect one's identity]

2377
01:24:21,820 --> 01:24:23,400
No, no, no.

2378
01:24:23,770 --> 01:24:24,970
[Is it exposed?]

2379
01:24:24,970 --> 01:24:25,950
[Lee Sooji]

2380
01:24:25,950 --> 01:24:26,060
[A total mess of disguises]

2381
01:24:26,060 --> 01:24:26,930
Lee Sooji.

2382
01:24:26,930 --> 01:24:28,410
[At this rate… will this even work…?]

2383
01:24:28,490 --> 01:24:28,630
A group activity for Secret Manito.

2384
01:24:28,630 --> 01:24:31,360
[A new mission is given to them]

2385
01:24:31,360 --> 01:24:33,310
[HQ: Your Secret Manito]

2386
01:24:33,310 --> 01:24:34,730
[HQ: is????]

2387
01:24:34,730 --> 01:24:36,570
[Beyond imagination — the identities of the Secret Manito…]

2388
01:24:36,570 --> 01:24:37,680
Really?

2389
01:24:39,910 --> 01:24:41,840
It feels like someone just came in.

2390
01:24:42,770 --> 01:24:43,990
What is this?

2391
01:24:45,300 --> 01:24:45,870
That's amazing.
